## Comments

### Don't comment what the code says — comment why
```typescript
// ✗ Useless comment — the code already says this
// Loop through messages
messages.forEach(message => { ... })

// ✓ Useful comment — explains a non-obvious decision
// We prepend the ISO timestamp before embedding so the vector
// carries temporal context — "what the user said on April 9"
// rather than just "what the user said"
const embeddingText = `[${message.createdAt.toISOString()}] ${message.content}`
```

### TODO comments always include what's needed before it gets done
```typescript
// TODO: remove this once calendar oauth is implemented
// For now we only write to Pem's internal task list
```

